{"tid":781461,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周永恒崩哭求阿Yu女兒原諒：對佢哋好大虧欠","createTime":"2018-08-16T02:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T10:56:21.000Z","uid":152476,"like":10,"dislike":962,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbd25819c72f023a40d4af29314c4f5c33226a0","tid":781461,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180816/2_614141_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180816%2F2_614141_0&d=0MmRsDG7u40qM6sWtv%2BP67%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6e65b0a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180816%2F2_614141_0&h=08a372af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180816/2_614141_0</a><br />\n<br />\n14年因為婚外情同家暴，周永恒自己拆散頭家。<br />\n<br />\n四年過去，他與阿Yu各自有新開始，他更剛跟大陸女友再婚。<br />\n<br />\n但在這時候，他才跟阿Yu講句：「對不起&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n對於這個遲來的道歉，阿Yu沉默了一會，只淡然說：「哦，過了四年才說這番說話，那麼有趣！」<br />\n<br />\n兩個女不想見他，他亦沒勇氣破冰，三父女差不多四年沒見面。他哭着說：「爸爸在這裡，好愛你們，雖然我不懂怎去做，爸爸在這裡&hellip;我做錯過甚麼，好多大家都會知。明明是自己錯，卻變成感情問題，沒有對錯。不接受自己錯，用個人智慧去繞道，不肯面對自己，對她們好大虧欠。」"},{"pid":"c482df60fc05507b49b3a00bab5487fa825effcb","tid":781461,"uid":706,"like":943,"dislike":7,"score":936,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:08:32.000Z","msg":"正宗煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無人想知呀<br />\n(Show Blocked User - 周永恒)"},{"pid":"d16d61bb02076129c4e26a206c3fc1dd6f29f11b","tid":781461,"uid":28327,"like":109,"dislike":10,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"搵2個女刷存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ec7debc7bf66ce4aa961c39f3bf42061b0c8c4